high_descs: Walk to stand in front of the sink in front of you to your right so you are in front of it facing it.
Pick up the apple closest to the head of lettuce in the sink.
Turn around and take a step then turn right and walk to the fridge then take a step to your left.
Chill the apple in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Take a big step to your left.
Put the cold apple in the garbage in front of you please.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple in the garbage.

high_descs: walk to the kitchen sink at the end of the room on the right
grab an apple out of the kitchen sink
turn left and walk over to the fridge on the left at the end of the room
place the apple inside the fridge, let the apple cool down, then take it back out
turn left and and walk over to the left side of the fridge on the right
place the apple inside of the blue recycling bin on the floor

high_descs: Move forward and to the right, to the sink.
Pick up the apple in the sink.
Turn around, bring the apple to the fridge on the right.
Chill the apple in the fridge.
Bring the chilled apple to the blue bin to the left of the fridge.
Put the chilled apple in the blue bin.
